#: src/welcome-window.c:81
msgid "<i>New in this Version:</i>"
msgstr "<i>New in this Version:</i>"

#: src/welcome-window.c:84
msgid ""
"This is <b>v0.79.10-pl6</b>. The [patchlevel series] are enhanced on top of the last upstream release to:\n"
"- add support for BD-R TL/QL and HD-DVD,\n"
"- add support for stripping ECC from ISOs,\n"
"- add an option to generate BD-R RS03 images with more redundancy and custom medium sizes,\n"
"- add an option to bruteforce search for RS03 roots on a custom medium size whose size has been forgotten,\n"
"- re-enable adaptive reading support,\n"
"- port the GUI to GTK3,\n"
"- ... and a lot more.\n"
"\n"
"Please refer to the <i>Help &gt; Change log</i> menu for all the details."
msgstr "This is <b>v0.79.10-pl6</b>. The [patchlevel series] are enhanced on top of the last upstream release to:\n- add support for BD-R TL/QL and HD-DVD,\n- add support for stripping ECC from ISOs,\n- add an option to generate BD-R RS03 images with more redundancy and custom medium sizes,\n- add an option to bruteforce search for RS03 roots on a custom medium size whose size has been forgotten,\n- re-enable adaptive reading support,\n- port the GUI to GTK3,\n- ... and a lot more.\n\nPlease refer to the <i>Help &gt; Change log</i> menu for all the details."

